source:
TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_SEQ_00<tab>Uin Nee will never tire of dreaming up new tasks for their favorite mortal.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>特殊ルール： レベルアジャスト受注クラス・ジョブ制限<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
※本クエストは受注時のクラス・ジョブでのみ進行します。

リダ・ラーンのウィン＝ニイには、夢があるようだ。

source: TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_TODO_00<tab>Obtain tufts of miniature mallow from near Lyhe Ghiah.
target: TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_TODO_00<tab>リェー・ギア城付近で<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8FF301 /var>を入手

source: TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the tufts of miniature mallow to Uin Nee.

TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_UINNEE_000_000<tab>Oh, hello there, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>! Apropos of absolutely nothing, have you ever been to Lyhe Ghiah? It's a most wonderful place, home to a magnificent castle and lovely balls of fluffy mallow that float up and down, to and fro in the gently rustling winds.
target:
TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_UINNEE_000_000<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>さんは、リェー・ギア城の周りに、
フワフワ～って、浮草が浮いているのは知ってる？
風を受けて、上下したり、くるくる回転したりしてるやつよ。

source: TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_UINNEE_000_001<tab>Well, I was thinking about what I could do to make the children's dreams that much sweeter, and that's when it hit me with all the force of a giant fluffball! I could fill them with poofy, puffy mallow! Wouldn't that just be the most delightful dream ever? Of course it would!
target:
TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_UINNEE_000_001<tab>ワタシ、あの浮草を、夢の中にも、
たくさん浮かばせてみたいと思うの！
見てるだけで、楽しい気分になること請け合いよ！

source: TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_UINNEE_000_002<tab>But to do that I'll need tufts of mallow, and I simply couldn't bear to take time out of my dreamspinning duties to flutter all the way over to Lyhe Ghiah! After all, what would the children do without me? It's a good thing you came here to offer your aid! That <var 1A 02 /var>is<var 1A 01 /var> why you came here, isn't it?
target:
TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_UINNEE_000_002<tab>そこでお願いなんだけれど、周辺に生えている、
「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8FF301 /var>」を採ってきてくれないかしら？
潰れないように、摘むときはそ～っと慎重にね！

source: TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_UINNEE_000_010<tab>Welcome back! Are those tufts of mallow bursting from your pocket, or are you just happy to see me? Or is it both? It's definitely both, isn't it?
target: TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_UINNEE_000_010<tab>「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8FF301 /var>」は、無事に手に入ったかしら？

source: TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_UINNEE_000_011<tab>I knew I could count on you. And just look at these fluffy little tufts! They might not strike you as much now, but once I've worked my magic, they'll sprout into airy balls of fantastic fluff fleecier than the thickest sheep's wool!
target:
TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_UINNEE_000_011<tab>これこれ、ご苦労さまっ！
今はまだ苗だけど、立派に育った浮草の綿毛って、
羊毛みたいにモッフモフしてて、気持ちいいのよね～♪

source: TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_UINNEE_000_012<tab>Yes, my dreamers will just love floating through the sky on massive clouds of mallow! Why, I'd even like to try it myself! Not that there's anything wrong about flying with good old-fashioned wings, of course. All the flitting and fluttering just gets a bit tiring from time to time, that's all. <yawn> I think I've earned myself a rest!
target:
TEXT_BANPIX108_03696_UINNEE_000_012<tab>羽で飛ぶのもいいけど、これに乗って、
夢の世界でゆったり浮かぶのも、きっと楽しいに違いないわ！
どうもありがとうね！
